@startuml
actor "Sinh viên" as Student
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "CourseController" as CC
participant "CourseService" as CS
participant "CourseRepository" as CR
database "Database" as DB

Student -> FE: Truy cập Dashboard
FE -> CC: GET /api/courses/student/{studentId}
activate CC

CC -> CS: getCoursesByStudentId(studentId)
activate CS

CS -> CR: findCoursesByStudentId(studentId)
activate CR
CR -> DB: SELECT * FROM courses c \nJOIN enrollments e ON c.id = e.course_id \nWHERE e.student_id = ?
DB --> CR: Danh sách Course Entities
CR --> CS: List<Course>
deactivate CR

CS -> CS: Map Course Entities to \nStudentCourseResponse
CS --> CC: List<StudentCourseResponse>
deactivate CS

CC --> FE: 200 OK (JSON List)
deactivate CC

FE -> FE: Cập nhật State (Redux/React State)
FE --> Student: Hiển thị danh sách khóa học (Tên, Mã môn, Giảng viên...)
@enduml